msgstr "Get information on deciding whether to switch to chezmoi"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-02-linux-dotfiles-management.rst:34
msgid "Bare‑repo 方式とは"
msgstr "What is Bare‑repo method?"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-02-linux-dotfiles-management.rst:35
msgid ""
"ホームディレクトリをそのままワークツリーにし、``$HOME/.dotfiles`` を **ベアリポジトリ** "
"として扱うシンプルな手法です。利点と欠点を整理すると"
msgstr ""
"This is a simple method that uses the home directory as a work tree and "
"treats ``$HOME/.dotfiles`` as a **bare repository**. Sorting out the "
"advantages and disadvantages"

